name: OBATALA
description: Obatala or “Orisa Nla” (known as Obatalá in Yorubaland (NIGERIA) and in Caribbean and South American Spanish and Oxalá in Brazil) is an orisha(gods). He is believed, according to Yoruba cosmology, to be the Sky Father and the creator of human bodies, which were brought to life by the smooth breath of Olodumare.(GOD)
